User Stories:
1. As an administrator, I want to be able to add new employees to the system.
2. As an administrator, I want to be able to edit employee details.
3. As an administrator, I want to be able to deactivate or reactivate employees as needed.
4. As an employee, I want to be able to clock in and clock out using the app.
5. As an employee, I want to view my own clock-in and clock-out history.
6. As an employee, I want to be able to view my total hours worked for a specific date range.
7. As an employee, I want to be able to change my current job.
8. As an administrator, I want to be able to view the clock-in and clock-out history for all employees.
9. As an administrator, I want to generate payroll reports based on the total hours worked.
10. As an administrator, I want to generate total hours for a specific job.